snippet.title: A Nightmare on Sesame Street Game Trailer
snippet.description:
I didn't make this trailer for my game, A Nightmare on Sesame Street, ReapeeRon did. This is his original video, https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=30bzidLmSK4 I just decided to make this into a trailer for the game. :)

Check the game out here! https://dave-microwaves-games.itch.io/a-nightmare-on-sesame-street

Also check out my latest horror game, TUNKY! https://dave-microwaves-games.itch.io/tunky
